3. Key Features Breakdown
A. Exterior Design & Build (02:00–03:30)

Material: 100% German polycarbonate (scratch-resistant, lightweight).

Aesthetic details: Textured finish, color options, premium leather handles.

Airline compatibility (reference attached list – “fits most major airlines”).

B. Size & Compliance (03:30–04:30)

Carry-On: 22” x 14” x 9” (36L) – Ideal for short trips.

Carry-On Plus: 23.2” x 15” x 10.2” (45L) – Expanded capacity for longer trips.

Highlight airline-friendly dimensions (show Airline_compatibility_2.png).

C. Weight (04:30–05:00)

Carry-On: 7.9 lbs / Carry-On Plus: 8.3 lbs.

Stress lightweight design despite durability.

D. Wheels & Mobility (05:00–06:00)

Tri-bearing 360° wheels: Silent, smooth glide (demo on tile/carpet).

Telescopic handle: Soft-grip, ergonomic adjustment.

E. Security & Zippers (06:00–07:00)

TSA-008 lock: Top-mounted for easy access.

YKK reverse coil zippers: Durability and color-matched design.

F. Interior Organization (07:00–09:00)

Luxurious interior: Anti-microbial lining, compression straps.

Included accessories: Laundry bag, shoe bags, personalization stickers.

Carry-On Plus: Extra space demo (fit for 7–10 days).

4. Packing Demo (09:00–11:00)
Carry-On: Pack for a 3–4 day trip (clothes, shoes, tech).

Carry-On Plus: Pack for a 7–10 day trip (add bulkier items).

Show compression straps in action.

