Lifetime Warranty: Highlight coverage (shell cracks, broken wheels/handles).

Key Limitations: Cosmetic wear excluded, non-transferable, requires proof of purchase.

6. Final Thoughts (12:00–13:00)
Pros: Lightweight, sleek design, silent wheels, airline compliance, lifetime warranty.

Cons: Cosmetic wear not covered, premium price point.

Verdict: Who should buy each size (frequent travelers vs. occasional).

